He is a event bus system that offer posting event to the subscriber who interesting on it;

0.0.1-SNAPSHOT
	use java reflect to invoke method.
	
	____________________					  _________
   | 					| 					 /		   \					 onEvent
   |					|	   Event		/			\				   / --------->Subscriber
   |	Publisher		|----------------> /	Event	 \	------------->/			   
   |					|	   post()	   \	 Bus	 /			      \	 onEvent
   |____________________|		   			\			/				   \---------->Subscriber
											 \_________/
	
